title: Arbor Skateboards :: Product Profiles - Zeppelin
description:
The Zeppelin is built around Gullwing Sidewinder trucks, with a narrow platform that delivers the rail-to-rail control needed for a supremely responsive ride and an exceptional carving experience.
Artist: Hunter Patrick
Artist: Nanami Cowdroy

L: 33.00” W: 8.50” WB: 23.50”
To learn more about the Zeppelin visit: arborcollective.com/skateboards/products/zeppelin/
